    "en": {
      "title": "Declining Marriages \u2013 Registrations drop by 85 percent",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "According to the Association of Registrars of Marriages, Births and Deaths, the decline in marriages is due to the fuel crisis and economic crisis.",
        "Susanta Hemasiri Ranasinghe, secretary of the Association of Registrars of Marriages, Births and Deaths, said that the number of marriage registrations has decreased by 85 percent so far this year compared to last year.",
        "In this regard, Secretary of the Association of Registrars of Marriages, Births and Deaths Susantha Hemasiri Ranasinghe commented,",
        "'This month is usually the month where most weddings take place. This month is usually a very stressful period especially for booking marriage halls. But not so this year.",
        "When looking at the forecasts available regarding marriage registration, the number of marriage registrations has fallen significantly.",
        "The situation where the date has been reserved for marriage registration is very rare. He said."
      ],
